Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.36,0:00:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.56,0:00:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢總將有完結的一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.86,0:00:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快樂的夢也是 恐怖的夢也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.20,0:00:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在溫暖的棉被中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.10,0:00:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為被母親搖醒而中斷的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.34,0:00:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直沒有改變的早上的景色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.07,0:00:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.60,0:00:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間的黃昏的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.95,0:01:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行著一段永遠的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.56,0:01:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的指尖繼續探索著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.47,0:01:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碎片發出光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.41,0:01:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊的抱住胸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.82,0:01:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找遺失的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.95,0:01:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用雙手的掌心確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.23,0:01:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相遇在新的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.57,0:01:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間開始流動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.42,0:02:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是記憶回復了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.49,0:02:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是想起自己的事\N然後回家了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.87,0:02:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…應該是這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.74,0:02:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要出門嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.37,0:02:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.74,0:02:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那門我就不上鎖了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.51,0:02:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「她們的想法」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.28,0:03:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.45,0:03:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.22,0:03:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 到哪裡去了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.02,0:03:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有可以回去的地方卻這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.53,0:03:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.50,0:03:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙在做什麼啊 讓人家擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.24,0:03:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請給我兩個肉包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.95,0:03:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 難道錢不夠嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.09,0:03:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.47,0:04:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然爬到這麼高的地方來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.09,0:04:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底要到哪裡去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.15,0:04:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的家在這種地方嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.44,0:04:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.32,0:04:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每個一人一半喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.62,0:05:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個都是一樣的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.56,0:05:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有可以去的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.66,0:05:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨隨便便被人飼養就算會幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.20,0:05:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是被拋棄時是會很痛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.34,0:05:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好累喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.04,0:05:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了找你還真辛苦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.84,0:05:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.08,0:05:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.98,0:05:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想睡在溫暖被窩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.19,0:05:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.69,0:05:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方睡會感冒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.83,0:05:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.17,0:05:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也要跟我們回去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.73,0:06:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.80,0:06:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我為什麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.54,0:06:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是祐一背妳回來的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.51,0:06:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的貓呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.51,0:06:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.85,0:06:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 一直看貓的話會遲到的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.78,0:06:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我現在就走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.99,0:06:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.09,0:06:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 在家裡的人\N應該要說“慢走”才對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.29,0:06:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以待在這裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.30,0:06:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠也可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.50,0:06:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.24,0:06:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 我走囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.78,0:07:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請慢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.48,0:07:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.55,0:07:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 對不起\N妳對貓過敏卻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.32,0:07:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的啦 我喜歡貓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.02,0:07:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我如果離家出走你會來找我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.90,0:07:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話了 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.50,0:07:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舞會的布告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.24,0:07:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舞會？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.61,0:07:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是每年的慣例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.44,0:07:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是沒有參加…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是全體參加的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.01,0:07:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是屬於學生會內部的活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.25,0:07:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們即使去也是怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.19,0:07:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“石膏像素描”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.46,0:07:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.76,0:07:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去買麵包了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.23,0:07:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麵包我就有了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.40,0:08:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能不是自己吃的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.41,0:08:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真想睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.92,0:08:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.29,0:08:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.46,0:08:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好玩嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.56,0:08:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡聽人這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之先進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,校舍裡面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.87,0:08:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.24,0:08:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.77,0:08:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.17,0:08:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感冒的人不能一直待在外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.41,0:08:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你感冒了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.91,0:08:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為昨晚在外面閒晃了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.62,0:08:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保重喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.25,0:08:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被病人說保重 真糗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.86,0:08:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.49,0:08:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舞會的排演吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.06,0:08:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我很憧憬喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.56,0:09:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從我看到我姐\N穿著舞會的禮服開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.83,0:09:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想\N穿著那樣漂亮的禮服跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.77,0:09:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩織 妳有姐姐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.81,0:09:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過沒有嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.61,0:09:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.81,0:09:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 頭髮很長而且是捲髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.12,0:09:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身材很好而且頭腦也很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.05,0:09:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.35,0:09:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美阪香里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.69,0:09:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了嗎？我沒有妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.73,0:09:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她 為什麼要這樣說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.17,0:09:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.23,0:09:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過妳也來參加舞會嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.57,0:09:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒辦法 沒有禮服…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.91,0:09:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果是跟祐一的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.01,0:09:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相澤 能不能收一下\N你自己的畫架啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.98,0:09:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.38,0:09:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.42,0:10:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.42,0:10:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛的女孩子是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香里的妹妹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.46,0:10:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.70,0:10:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別裝不知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.90,0:10:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是有個那麼可愛的妹妹嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.77,0:10:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳誤會了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.41,0:10:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.48,0:10:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在要去參加社團的活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.98,0:10:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要打擾我好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.35,0:10:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼搞的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.29,0:10:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃飯好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.54,0:10:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 請不要客氣盡量吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.24,0:10:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.61,0:10:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼合格啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.92,0:11:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能當我的新娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.19,0:11:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話\N大家都要當你的新娘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.62,0:11:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是香里也這麼好親近就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.26,0:11:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也有一個不好親近的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.23,0:11:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞她以前就是這樣了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.77,0:11:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.04,0:11:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.14,0:11:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也不常見到小舞笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.94,0:11:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.55,0:11:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.58,0:11:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須要變得更開朗才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.95,0:11:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為一直這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.69,0:11:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才會被貼上是在晚上打破玻璃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.59,0:11:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不良少女的標籤吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.29,0:11:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞 笑看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再開朗點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.87,0:11:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.87,0:11:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.10,0:11:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須打從心底改變才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.71,0:12:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.28,0:12:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.35,0:12:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,參加舞會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.22,0:12:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著漂亮的禮服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓人看到妳優雅的跳著舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.65,0:12:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上會成為熱門人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.09,0:12:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也就不會有人\N叫妳不良少女了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.69,0:12:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行的啦 祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.29,0:12:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.53,0:12:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是改變壞形象的\N最好機會嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.56,0:12:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.46,0:12:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我跟小舞一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.73,0:12:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有可以穿去舞會的禮服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.74,0:12:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.77,0:12:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊\N因為我們是平凡的女孩子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.11,0:12:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.37,0:12:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的川澄舞受歡迎計畫\N才剛決定就宣告破滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.35,0:12:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說那些不知所謂的計畫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.15,0:12:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.99,0:12:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然祐一這麼為小舞著想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.62,0:12:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.76,0:12:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會向我朋友拜託看看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.60,0:12:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有拜託妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.70,0:12:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.30,0:13:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一穿燕尾服就行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.64,0:13:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也要參加嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.20,0:13:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不參加嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.41,0:13:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會參加吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.72,0:13:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.89,0:13:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眉毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.46,0:13:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是眉毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.19,0:13:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.79,0:13:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 三毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.76,0:13:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鼻毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.06,0:13:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再說“毛”了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.37,0:13:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貓的名字決定了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 決定叫紅鬍子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.11,0:13:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫鯛魚燒怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.44,0:13:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的名字…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.61,0:13:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳從那進來的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.61,0:13:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛在買東西時遇到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.41,0:13:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又遇到了啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.15,0:13:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機會難得\N留下來吃晚餐吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.52,0:13:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也稍微客氣一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.12,0:13:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 名字是吃的東西\N不是很可愛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.72,0:13:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,譬如說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.16,0:14:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草莓或巧克力啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.26,0:14:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉包或豆沙包啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？\N不行嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.70,0:14:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 叫皮羅斯基如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.87,0:14:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,澤渡皮羅斯基
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.64,0:14:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,取發音簡稱皮羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.11,0:14:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣 很可愛吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皮羅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.58,0:14:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 牠也說很喜歡這名字喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.52,0:14:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.38,0:14:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始你就叫皮羅喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.49,0:14:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 皮羅斯基是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.42,0:14:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俄羅斯一種包肉的炸麵包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.63,0:14:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是像肉包的東西嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.66,0:14:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要當事人喜歡不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.53,0:14:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.00,0:14:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.54,0:14:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 只是有點站不穩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要幫忙嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.34,0:14:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.71,0:14:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.55,0:14:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.42,0:15:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 亞由…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.46,0:15:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊已經好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要晚回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.56,0:15:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先跟家裡聯絡一下比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 一起來看漫畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳自己一個人看啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.00,0:15:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 一起來折紙飛機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.31,0:15:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳自己一個人折啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.97,0:15:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.24,0:15:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.94,0:15:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.78,0:15:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是打錯電話了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.45,0:15:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是去買東西了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.22,0:15:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們丟下妳一個去吃好料的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.43,0:15:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.76,0:15:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.70,0:15:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果方便的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.10,0:15:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞由今晚也在這裡過夜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.30,0:15:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不錯喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.54,0:15:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我的房間鋪床棉被就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.46,0:16:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要出門嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.60,0:16:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以打擾一下嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.90,0:16:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊 名雪呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.90,0:16:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鑽進棉被裡就馬上睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.47,0:16:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.71,0:16:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.18,0:16:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨跟名雪都是好人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.04,0:16:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然說這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.95,0:16:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很久沒有跟大家一起\N邊談天邊吃飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.65,0:16:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很快樂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.35,0:16:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.26,0:16:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還記得七年前的事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.83,0:16:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給因為母親不在而哭泣的我\N鯛魚燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.87,0:16:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真的很溫暖 很甜 很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.31,0:17:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還記得七年前的味道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.68,0:17:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然記得啊 因為我非常高興喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.61,0:17:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.58,0:17:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也記得喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.75,0:17:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞由 妳為我親手做的餅乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.42,0:17:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的像炭一樣黑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.83,0:17:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那根本不能吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.33,0:17:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欺負人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.50,0:17:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.07,0:17:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一也真的都沒變呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.51,0:17:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種壞心眼的地方也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.11,0:17:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.21,0:17:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.98,0:17:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依然是我喜歡的祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.95,0:17:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說的這個喜歡\N不是那個喜歡啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.65,0:17:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛這麼慌張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.66,0:17:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 皮羅牠…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.26,0:17:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在發抖…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.83,0:17:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看牠好像很冷\N就把牠放到棉被裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.37,0:18:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是感冒吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.97,0:18:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感冒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.17,0:18:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 去燒熱水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.11,0:18:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用熱水袋幫牠保暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.81,0:18:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在上面舖上毛巾然後把貓放進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.91,0:18:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這種時候這樣做是最重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.25,0:18:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.05,0:18:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一你好像很熟練呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.32,0:18:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我小時候也養過動物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.52,0:18:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,養了什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.93,0:18:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的確有養啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.66,0:18:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.54,0:18:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安 妳起的真早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.64,0:18:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 要晨練啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.94,0:18:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,練習服還沒乾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.65,0:18:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.05,0:18:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題才怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.48,0:18:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.15,0:18:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像還在睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.85,0:18:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨是怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.80,0:19:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.27,0:19:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…還沒弄早餐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.04,0:19:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.11,0:19:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好燙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.51,0:19:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 只是感冒而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.18,0:19:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不躺著不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.98,0:19:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞由？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.02,0:19:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我討厭這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.39,0:19:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.43,0:19:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.73,0:19:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭每個人都離開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.33,0:19:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.37,0:19:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨才不會離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.57,0:19:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 不會有事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.42,0:19:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 你去學校吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.18,0:19:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞由？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.25,0:20:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會照顧秋子阿姨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.29,0:20:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.52,0:20:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使我叫妳不要\N妳也聽不進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.19,0:20:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.33,0:20:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會從學校打電話回來\N秋子阿姨就拜託妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.87,0:20:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.94,0:20:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該只是感冒 不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.04,0:20:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎已經沒有燒的那麼嚴重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.61,0:20:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是要吃點東西才能吃藥\N那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.42,0:20:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能拜託妳作午餐了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是她的料理…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在只能相信她了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.13,0:20:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？\N我在這裡告訴你做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.50,0:20:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先 先把材料切細
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.04,0:20:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將火關掉後加入雞蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.86,0:21:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.19,0:21:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.59,0:21:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.60,0:21:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.06,0:21:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒問題了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.13,0:21:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托這個孩子的福…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.87,0:21:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一直照顧著我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.41,0:21:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很努力的照顧皮羅喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.45,0:21:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.95,0:21:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.42,0:21:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞由 謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.27,0:22:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
